snippet.title: Bulwark: Falconeer Chronicles - Official Trade, Tribute and Spoils Reveal Trailer
snippet.description: The Trade, Tribute and Spoils update for Bulwark: Falconeer Chronicles brings a new navigational compass, the new Splinters currency that you can use to repair your fleet and buy extractors, and new diplomatic events to the strategy city-builder game. Watch the latest trailer for Bulwark: Falconeer Chronicles to see what to expect with the free Trade, Tribute and Spoils update, coming soon. Bulwark: Falconeer Chronicles is available now on PS5 (PlayStation 5), PS4 (PlayStation 4), Steam, EGS, GoG, Utomik, Xbox Series X/S, and Xbox One.
